{"tid":2061810,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"一口氣睇完本漫畫空虛到好似失戀咁","createTime":"2020-06-12T16:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T17:12:59.000Z","uid":136414,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"da129de11c5091c31d70882295a61b8180f58b16","tid":2061810,"uid":136414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"呢排無聊搵左本漫畫睇(河合莊)<br />\n一星期之內由第一卷直落睇到最尾十一卷結局<br />\n相比追連載隔幾個星期先睇一次 個感情投入冇咁深<br />\n睇完河合莊個人失落到頂唔順 好似唔肯接受現實咁不停搵仲有冇後續短篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 結果當然係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來以為睇d 戀愛喜劇個人會開心D 點知係相反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n格硬返到現實更加辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f79a97fc5db0490e45c86ad83bd7f132ea91188d","tid":2061810,"uid":136414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:07:30.000Z","msg":"post完出黎已經覺得自己有D 戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1ea1f81bcc4cb5dfcbd2c50d1069442a4c22964","tid":2061810,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"Iktf"},{"pid":"08649597e551bd10b0f96957b430e5007fed9961","tid":2061810,"uid":304926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:56:33.000Z","msg":"我明，所以通常會睇完一套，立即去睇下一套沖淡個感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e72f802494a1220e773029aa3a15f718ff10d30","tid":2061810,"uid":136414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f1ea1f81bcc4cb5dfcbd2c50d1069442a4c22964","tid":2061810,"uid":17352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:55:06.000Z","msg":"Iktf"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T17:29:31.000Z","msg":"係咪毒L先會咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08e8899f6d77a5093a4a9fc6802b4b80fab27e2","tid":2061810,"uid":136414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score